  "title": "Events & Sales Marketing [FRESH GRADUATE]",
  "description": "<h1><strong>🌟 We’re Hiring: Brand Promoting Crew</strong></h1><p><strong>Join us and turn every event into a story worth sharing — where your creativity brings brands to life.</strong><br />As part of our Brand Promoting Crew, you’ll be the spark that connects people with the brands they love. If you’re energetic, friendly, and enjoy engaging with others, this is the perfect role for you.</p><h2><strong>✨ What You’ll Do</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Represent the brand at events, roadshows, and promotions</p></li><li><p>Engage customers with confidence and enthusiasm</p></li><li><p>Demonstrate products and share key brand messages</p></li><li><p>Encourage sign-ups, sampling, and participation in activities</p></li><li><p>Assist with booth setup, displays, and event operations</p></li><li><p>Capture customer feedback and help improve event experiences</p></li></ul><h2><strong>✨ Who We’re Looking For</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Outgoing, approachable, and energetic personality</p></li><li><p>Strong communication and customer-service skills</p></li><li><p>Comfortable speaking with people from all backgrounds</p></li><li><p>Able to stand, move, and work in lively environments</p></li><li><p>Experience in events, promotions, or retail is a plus (but not required!)</p></li><li><p>Willing to work on weekends, evenings, and event schedules</p></li></ul><h2><strong>✨ What You’ll Get</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Attractive daily/hourly pay + incentives</p></li><li><p>Fun, social, and creative work environment</p></li><li><p>Opportunities to work at exciting events and brand activations</p></li><li><p>Free training — no experience needed</p></li><li><p>Flexible schedule (event-based)</p></li></ul><h2><strong>📩 Ready to Bring Brands to Life?</strong></h2><p>Send your resume or short introduction to <strong>[Your Email]</strong><br /><strong></strong></p>",
